 Scowl 签约 Dead Oceans 并分享激烈的新单曲“Special” https://www.nme.com/news/music/scowl-sign-to-dead-oceans-and-share-fierce-new-single-special-3800768?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=scowl-sign-to-死海和分享激烈新单曲特别Anagricel DuranTue, 08 Oct 2024 16:01:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsHardcoreRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3800768 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="皱眉头。图片来源：西尔肯·温伯格" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队的最后一张专辑是他们 2023 年的 EP“Psychic Dance Routine”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scowl-sign-to-dead-oceans-and-share-fierce-new-single-special-3800768">Scowl 签约 Dead Oceans 并分享激烈的新单曲“Special”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="皱眉头。图片来源：西尔肯·温伯格" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scowl.-Credit-Silken-Weinberg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Scowl">Scowl</a>分享了他们激烈的新单曲“Special”，这是他们在新厂牌 Dead Oceans 下的首次发行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/scowl-band-psychic-dance-routine-ep-review-radar-3426320">Scowl – “Psychic Dance Routine” EP 评论：能量的胜利爆发</a></strong></li></ul><p>由获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>提名的 Will Yip 制作，他还参与了乐队 EP Psychic Dance Routine 的制作，并由 Rich Costey（ <a href="/artists/Fiona-Apple">Fiona Apple</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Deftones">Deftones</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Vampire-Weekend">Vampire Weekend</a> ）混音。《Special》中主唱 Kat Moss 演唱了<em>“Caught running away Again / Thought by now”</em>在敲击的鼓声和爆炸性的吉他连复段中<em>，我明白了/我的毁灭是地狱/这是对活着的绝望”</em> ，质疑她真正想要的是什么。</p><p>莫斯在新闻稿中谈到这首歌曲时说道：“最初，玛拉基（吉他手格林）在我们英国巡演时发送了演示版。科尔（Glibert）在鼓上添加了他的耀眼，贝利（卢波，贝斯手）指挥了桥段，最后米奇（贝斯手）制作了他的主奏。 “特殊”是神风特攻队。</p><p> “歌词是通过询问‘你真正想要什么？’来威胁观众。”显然是绝望地回答我自己的问题“我真正想要什么？”但答案很简单，我想要感觉还活着。” </p><p><iframe title="皱眉 - 特别版（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CGzyxGSqaE4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>由西尔肯·温伯格 (Silken Weinberg) 执导，在这首歌的随附视频中，乐队玩了一个游戏，莫斯最终选择了一根短棍，这意味着她将成为被追捕的人。当她躲藏起来时，乐队的其他成员继续追捕她。</p><p>乐队还宣布他们已与 Dead Oceans 厂牌签约，该厂牌是<a href="/artists/Phoebe-Bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Mitski">Mitski</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Japanese-Breakfast">Japanese Breakfast</a>等歌手的故乡。</p><p> Scowl 的最后一张专辑是他们 2023 年的 EP“Psychic Dance Routine”。在对该项目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/scowl-band-psychic-dance-routine-ep-review-radar-3426320">四星评价</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>表示：“将《通灵舞蹈套路》称为对皱眉声音的重新发明有些夸张，但确实正在发生演变。但这张 EP 并不完全是为了听起来不像现在的硬核音乐中的其他任何东西。这些歌曲散发着乐队的欢笑、激情和自信，他们知道自己已经解锁了一些特别的东西。”</p><p>今年夏天早些时候，Scowl 等乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bands-who-are-boycotting-download-2024-come-together-for-palestine-fundraiser-gig-in-birmingham-3764622">抵制了 2024 年下载音乐节，原因是该音乐节与与以色列有联系的巴克莱银行有合作关系</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scowl-sign-to-dead-oceans-and-share-fierce-new-single-special-3800768">Scowl 签约 Dead Oceans 并分享激烈的新单曲“Special”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
