oads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VampireWeekend-cover-Fall-Out-Boy-Sugar-Were-Goin-Down-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">Vampire Weekend</a>最近在纽约的一场演出中简短翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">Fall Out Boy</a>的经典单曲“Sugar, We’re Goin Down”。观看下面的视频。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">吸血鬼周末——“只有上帝在我们之上”评论：回到纽约</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末（10 月 5 日和 6 日），这支纽约乐队在麦迪逊广场花园举行了两场返校演出，作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-announce-massive-2024-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3588656">他们当前北美巡演</a>的一部分，以支持他们的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">《Only God Was Below Us》</a> 。</p><p>最近的音乐会见证了埃兹拉·科尼格 (Ezra Koenig) 及其合作者。作为安可曲的一部分，快速翻唱众多著名歌曲。上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-vampire-weekend-beck-and-st-vincent-respond-to-chappell-roan-hot-to-go-meme-3797748">他们挑战了 Chappell Roan 的热门歌曲“Hot To Go!”向持续的病毒式传播趋势致敬</a>。</p><p>同样的表演还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a>等乐队的经典作品版本。最近，吸血鬼周末 (Vampire Weekend) 演绎了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Tears For Fears</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-strokes">The Strokes</a>等歌曲。</p><p>在 10 月 5 日举行的首场 MSG 音乐会上，乐队为观众表演了 Fall Out Boy 的副歌《Sugar, We&#39;re Goin Down》。简短的封面以 Koenig 唱歌和弹奏电吉他开始，不久之后又引入了鼓和钢琴。</p><p> Fall Out Boy 于 2005 年发行了第二张专辑《From Under the Cork Tree》的主打单曲《Sugar...》，随后在社交媒体上做出了回应。他们分享了当时的粉丝拍摄片段，并配上标题：“甜心，我们要变成朋克了<a href="https://twitter.com/vampireweekend?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1842972999173247222%7Ctwgr%5Ed16601788e1d416bb3f65bb1bb0b768cb321af71%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fpost.php%3Fpost%3D3800703action%3Dedit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@vampireweekend</a> 。”</p><p>查看此处的帖子：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我有吸血鬼周末去玩糖，我们将于 2024 年 10 月 5 日在麦迪逊广场花园被美国摇滚乐队 Fallout Boy 击败<a href="https://t.co/uUK7kFggp9">pic.twitter.com/uUK7kFggp9</a></p><p> — izzy ♡又名 2008fobstan *✧･ﾟ:* (@2008fobstan) <a href="https://twitter.com/2008fobstan/status/1842768318966497727?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">糖，我们要朋克了<a href="https://twitter.com/vampireweekend?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@vampireweekend</a> <a href="https://t.co/NSf29QCCIT">pic.twitter.com/NSf29QCCIT</a></p><p> - 打倒男孩 (@falloutboy) <a href="https://twitter.com/falloutboy/status/1842972999173247222?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在第一场 MSG 演出的主舞台上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-vampire-weekend-cover-billy-joels-scenes-from-an-italian-restaurant-at-madison-square-garden-3800019">Vampire Weekend 翻唱了 Billy Joel 的《Scenes From An Italian Re